# Brand Identity System

*Built from Pinterest mood board analysis + market positioning research · Updated April 2026 · Version 2*

> **Hero headline (primary):** "The same peanut butter you love, designed to drizzle."
> 

Spoonless is the format upgrade peanut butter has always needed. Not a wellness product, not a kids' brand — a drizzle-first, clean-label condiment that treats itself like extra virgin olive oil treats itself. Premium without being precious. Playful without being silly. The jar is gone. The squeeze is everything. For peanut butter lovers, finally. Everything you love about peanut butter, now in a drizzleable format. 

